{"tid":948482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔係啩？】俄羅斯最強AI智能機械人 被發現原來人扮","createTime":"2018-12-20T06:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T10:13:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"05caeb5df709dd419cd87d13c54eaab37b946a03","tid":948482,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:08:00.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族果然乜都做得出，最近呢單新聞令人大開眼界，話說有隻機械人「Boris」早前上咗俄羅斯電視台「Russia 24」節目，由於像真度極高，仲識模仿人類跳舞同回應主持提問，好快就成為大家嘅討論焦點。不過之後網上有人質疑，點解一直無聽過俄羅斯開發咁勁嘅機械人，過咗無幾耐，有人竟然喺一張相度發現隻機械人有「頸」嘅！入嚟有詳情。<br />\n睇返張相，有「頸」嘅機械人，即係話係人扮啦。而同時間，亦有網民喺IG搵到一個男人影自己扮機械人嘅相，原來呢隻叫「Boris」嘅機械人，係一間叫Show Robots嘅公司造出嚟嘅機械人服裝，售價$4000美金，內置變聲器，發光裝置，重10公斤，聲稱就算好似平常一樣行走，都會睇落似機械人嘅動作，嘩！勁到呢。不過究竟點解電視台「Russia 24」節目會話佢係「機械人」呢？就暫時都無人知道嘞。<br />\n呢套機械人服裝，售價$4000美金，內置變聲器，發光裝置，重10公斤，聲稱就算好似平常一樣行走，都會睇落似機械人嘅動作，嘩！勁到呢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tOlDIsZBXlYL_AXKmZwP5w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDMz/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant/homerun/gameover.com.hk/444492025d11b54754404957b767f4ce\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtOlDIsZBXlYL_AXKmZwP5w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDMz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant%2Fhomerun%2Fgameover.com.hk%2F444492025d11b54754404957b767f4ce&h=44497c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6aiOubDLELFnot1OGAWspw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9Mzg4/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant/homerun/gameover.com.hk/bfc7ad865d988bb424aa66dc2d4013df\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F6aiOubDLELFnot1OGAWspw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9Mzg4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant%2Fhomerun%2Fgameover.com.hk%2Fbfc7ad865d988bb424aa66dc2d4013df&h=f4fbe49b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UbpOoIm8sOG6qJV68sXw1A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NzE2/http://media.zenfs.com/